assignments.value:
=Hey, just noticed there wasn't a follow-up email to {{ $('Only Follow Ups').item.json.attendees.find(x => !x.self).email }} after your last call a few days ago.

Here's are a few available slots to book the next call.
{{
$json.output.slots
  .filter(slot => !DateTime.fromISO(slot.start).isWeekend())
  .map(slot => `* ${DateTime.fromISO(slot.start).format('cccc, DDD @ hh:mm')} - ${DateTime.fromISO(slot.end).format('hh:mm')}`)
.join('\n')
}}

Let me know which I should book or let me know if it's okay to dismiss.
